name: Make Your own badge
description:
Make your own badges by following these three simple steps.
1.	Select an image you want on your badge
2.	Email your image, your name and number of badges wanted to this email address badgeboutique@hotmail.co.uk 
3.	Simply purchase the number of badges you wish
You may be asked to clarify your address after you image has been received.
You can send us more than one image, but please specify how many badges you want of each image.
We cannot put any images that are copyright on a badge.
